ExternalData.Subtitlesect: Extension of the International Coffee Agreement, 1983*
ExternalData.EIF: 1 October 1989, in accordance with paragraph 5 and 6 of Resolution No. 347 adopted by the International Coffee Council on 3 July 1989. The Agreement was superseded on 1 October 1991 by the International Coffee Agreement, 1983 adopted by the International Coffee Council on 16 September 1982, as modified and extended by Resolution No. 352 of 28 September 1990 [see chapter XIX.25 c)].
